---
import '../styles/components/byo.css';
---

<section class="byo">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="byo-inner">
      <div class="byo-k">持</div>
      <div class="byo-text">
        <em>Bring</em> your own video. <em>Bring</em> your own subs.
        <span class="sub">
          MoeKoder does not include — and will never include — anime, manga, or subtitle files. You
          point it at an MKV and an ASS file from <b>your own library</b>, it hands you back a
          burned MP4. That's the whole deal.
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="byo-seal">
        <b>自分で持って来る</b>
        BYO · bring your own<br />
        no content · no piracy<br />
        you = the librarian
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
